ng add @nguniversal/express-engine

Si erreur au moment de l'installation:

- Remove the package node-modules
- Remove the file package-lock.json
- Run the command "npm install"
- Run this command "npm install @nguniversal/express-engine --legacy-peer-deps"
    If the package "@nguniversal/express-engine" will be installed, without creating files "server.ts" and
    "app.server.module.ts", then
- Run the command "ng add @nguniversal/express-engine"
